{"tid":865614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身纏逾200萬元冰毒闖關　柬埔寨抵港兩旅客斷正","createTime":"2018-10-17T07:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T10:04:27.000Z","uid":75969,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9b0882822b4766290c6dafcf4c47baf9b03234","tid":865614,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181017/photo/bkn-20181017150547410-1017_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181017155215\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181017%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181017150547410-1017_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181017155215&h=e3570d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關機場科人員，本周一(15日)在赤鱲角香港國際機場，截查2名從柬埔寨金邊乘飛機抵港的20歲及22歲男旅客，在他們的胸前、後背及大腿，搜出4包以繃帶纏着的懷疑冰毒，共重約4公斤，估計市值共約210萬港元，海關人員隨即將他們拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n案件其後交由海關毒品調查科接手跟進，經進一步調查後，2名男子被控一項販運危險藥物罪名，明日(18日)在西九龍裁判法院提堂，海關將進一步調查毒品來源及去向。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181017/photo/bkn-20181017150547410-1017_00822_001_02b.jpg?20181017155215\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181017%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181017150547410-1017_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20181017155215&h=57adf1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">檢獲的懷疑冰毒。(馬竟峯攝)<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181017/bkn-20181017150547410-1017_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181017%2Fbkn-20181017150547410-1017_00822_001.html&d=Z1qCflbjvdOU9%2BWWpJONNv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=b5b6ec55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181017/bkn-20181017150547410-1017_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a66741fbabb6ed65576fe99bd509df8acda922c5","tid":865614,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:58:48.000Z","msg":"運毒好心都運去北歐啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj